</row>
<row valign="middle">
<entry valign="middle" align="left">milliliter (mL)</entry><entry valign="middle" align="left">= 0.001 L (exact, definition)<newline/>= 1 cm<sup>3</sup> (exact, definition)</entry>
</row>
